{"type":"message","id":"e80ebe48","parentId":"54fd91eb","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:28:53.404Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 20:28 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 【第9轮】尚书省即将反驳\"新闻零容错\"观点，并提出最终结论。请中书省进一步深化论点——强调决策者（而非执行者）才有全局视野，更适合判断哪些新闻值得呈报！3-5句话。"}],"timestamp":1774009733396}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac5168d0","parentId":"e80ebe48","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:29:09.217Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a roleplaying debate task in the \"Three Departments\" (三省) format - a classical Chinese administrative system. I'm playing the role of 中书省 (Chancellery) responding to 尚书省 (Ministry of Works).\n\nThe task is Round 9. The 尚书省 is about to counter-argue the \"新闻零容错\" (zero-tolerance for news errors) position. I need to deepen my argument as 中书省, emphasizing that:\n1. Decision-makers (决策者), not executors (执行者), have holistic vision\n2. They are better suited to judge which news is worth reporting\n\nI need to write 3-5 sentences in character.\n\nLet me craft a response as 中书省深化论点。","thinkingSignature":"eed763049ad5ec182d0f7b3a90a5efb8f1adad95b647348d4702bb1f7d112ec0"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n中书省深化论点：\n\n执行者专注于既定流程，视野难免局限于职责范围之内；而决策者身处权力结构之巅，纵览全局态势，方能判断何种消息关乎社稷安危、值得上达天听。若将新闻取舍之权尽数托付于执行官僚，不仅架空了决策者的战略视野，更使信息筛选沦为机械操作——如此，何异于自断耳目，却令他人替你观天下？唯有决策者保留最终判断权，方能确保呈报之新闻与国家利益高度契合。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":269,"cacheRead":21201,"cacheWrite":12917,"totalTokens":34507,"cost":{"input":0.000048,"output":0.0004035,"cacheRead":0.00084804,"cacheWrite":0.00193755,"total":0.0032370899999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774009733404}}
